Steps to install keysig:

Requirements:
Keysig requires PHP5+ with GD and MySQL4+

1) Create a MySQL database called keysig
2) Run the two SQL statements in the keysig.sql file
3) After the tables have been created successfully remove the keysig.sql file
4) Create a new user for the keysig database and update your database settings in the /includes/database.php file
5) The "tmp" directory under the keysig folder much be writeable by the web user.  Chmod it with appropriate
	permissions so that the libchart graphs can be generated and landed in this location. 
	
For additional assistance stop by our support forums - http://forum.brilaps.com/.